---
import Slide from "../components/Slide.astro";
import FingerspellDemo from "../components/FingerspellDemo.astro";
---

<Slide animate={false}>
	<h2>🎥 Fingerspelling → subtitles</h2>
	<FingerspellDemo />
	<p class="caveat fragment">
		Honesty break: fingerspelling ≠ sign language. Real ASL has grammar, motion and facial expression — full
		translation is still open research. This is a building block.
	</p>
	<aside class="notes">
		Spell a short word without J or Z (they need motion): "HELLO", "ZENIKA" won't work — use "HI" or "DEMO". Pause
		~1.5s with the hand down to end a word. Press 'c' to clear. If letters misfire, samples were recorded on
		/calibrate — lighting matters.
	</aside>
</Slide>

<style>
	.caveat {
		font-size: 0.45em;
		color: #fbbf24;
		max-width: 80%;
		margin-inline: auto;
	}
</style>
